{"tid":2400440,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭回應英領雙重國籍問題：重申1996年已訂明被中國人條文 除非已聲明及獲確認外國國籍","createTime":"2021-02-09T03:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T09:16:12.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c90e15dde2fb09e4463a7db21a756d1b741c3718","tid":2400440,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥指人大常委會定明雙重國籍人士在港不受外國領事保護<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥，回應英國駐港總領事館指，由於香港不承雙重國籍，可能無法為同時擁有英國及中國國籍的人士，提供領事保護。林鄭月娥指，有關安排應參考人大常委會1996年就國籍法在香港實施的決定，指明除非有外國國籍人士，聲明及獲確認外國國籍，否則仍被視為中國公民，不享有外國領事保護；屬於國際法的維也納條約法公約(Vienna Convention)亦指出，在包括中國在內，不承認雙重國籍的國家，公民不會享有外國領事保護，有關安排是國際慣常做法。<br />\n<br />\n北京與特區政府上月宣布，不再承認BNO護照作為旅行證件及身份證明，反制英國政府開放BNO持有人申請入籍。英國駐港總領事館昨日在網頁更新旅遊指引，指得知香港與中國其他城市一樣，不承認雙重國籍，若同時擁有英國及中國國籍的人士，即使持英國護照進入香港，亦會被視為中國公民，在這個情況下，英國領事館可能不能提供領事協助，提醒如果已放棄中國國籍的人士，應帶備相關證明。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2378412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2378412&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=cba1b8a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2378412</a>"},{"pid":"a3f5b67459c00b9fbc4bad519ed720992d9dde93","tid":2400440,"uid":18477,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:10:59.000Z","msg":"修頓球場又要打蛇餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次係resign nmslese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f089bdf0ff7080aace61fe72a6766f1c1d52e04c","tid":2400440,"uid":267283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"姐係肯定3月開會會處理雙重國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時唔知會唔會只係針對BNO"},{"pid":"b249f37e816f4734aa0902af8e9b3989e4bf9652","tid":2400440,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:16:00.000Z","msg":"歷史文件"},{"pid":"c4de702e5063ad8462cfbd6a47cdd36270bd4788","tid":2400440,"uid":11291,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:17:45.000Z","msg":"媽咪，咁我點算呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YPTQP2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYPTQP2b.jpg&h=78391d39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6479e2a8179e57efb0dd49c2ed19084a844c8a3","tid":2400440,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪要排隊取消中國籍"},{"pid":"11a9c1eff2fe0b010c4fb1ba202a058f0853b940","tid":2400440,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a3f5b67459c00b9fbc4bad519ed720992d9dde93","tid":2400440,"uid":18477,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:10:59.000Z","msg":"修頓球場又要打蛇餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次係resign nmslese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:22:09.000Z","msg":"拎左BC 你先再去修頓排隊啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aaaac348d02ad1f8718a993d3e351154f021f9c","tid":2400440,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11a9c1eff2fe0b010c4fb1ba202a058f0853b940","tid":2400440,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a3f5b67459c00b9fbc4bad519ed720992d9dde93","tid":2400440,"uid":18477,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:10:59.000Z","msg":"修頓球場又要打蛇餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次係resign nmslese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:22:09.000Z","msg":"拎左BC 你先再去修頓排隊啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:23:08.000Z","msg":"首先攞住chinada passport嘅都有幾十萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41dd8a62b050b59ccca8497507ce4e59d3a8661b","tid":2400440,"uid":27915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:25:08.000Z","msg":"拜年問下啲美國澳洲藍絲親戚放唔放棄中國藉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b557eb02027a4443df68d79e8cab1ceebbd1a9","tid":2400440,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:25:39.000Z","msg":"可能係出大絕，封城，有 BNO / BC 就算撤僑都唔比你走，參考上年 武漢封城：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-51306996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-51306996&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=cdf3c8be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-51306996&h=469e89c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-51306996</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">中國不承認雙重國籍，但英國允許雙重國籍的存在。中國不允許雙重國籍護照持有人通過撤僑通道離開中國。<br />\n<br />\n來自約克的弗朗西斯（Natalie Francis）說，她被告知必須將三歲的兒子留在中國，因為兒子有中國護照。</span><br />\n<br />\n她說：「接到電話時，我無語了。」<br />\n<br />\n在武漢做英語老師的弗朗西斯補充說：「我不知道誰能解決這個問題，但請不要忘記我們。」<br />\n<br />\n來自英國諾森伯蘭郡的塞德爾（Jeff Siddle）說，他和女兒可以坐上星期四返英的航班，但他的中國妻子不行。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府正在敦促中國允許英國公民和他們的英中雙重國籍家庭成員離開中國。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部發言人說：「我們的首要任務是讓英國公民和家人能在一起，我們已向中國當局緊急提出這一要求。」<br />\n<br />\n英國已就雙國籍問題於1月28日向中方提出交涉。"},{"pid":"d0c88f514b39898fc3ed6ae960c7f4cb9caa583a","tid":2400440,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警號已經響起咗！<span class=\"red\">越著時間過去，離開香港將會日漸困難</span>，大時代中不能存有饒幸之心，成日同自己講冇事既、冇事既個d人，就係走唔切，困咗係東德既人。<span class=\"red\">總之任何人，有得即走，特別高風險人士一定要最早走，其他人遲極唔可以遲過外國撤僑，外國第一個國家撤僑你就要跟住飛。外國唔會一次過撤，會比時間同signal香港人走先。</span>切記你係難民唔係移民。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪好好奇美國點解得把口唔出手制裁？我話你知幾時先制裁、有冇可能封關、應唔應該走、幾時要走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2093986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2093986</a><br />\n<br />\n(分析)仲有幾耐入東突(新疆)模式，見到咩警告要流亡？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1980175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1980175</a><br />\n<br />\n香港簡易流亡手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/478029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/478029</a><br />\n<br />\n[借古鑑今] 中國因逃亡潮於 1951 年 2 月 15 日鎖關，香港因 BNO 鎖關的憂慮正響歐美之間蔓延！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2390806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2390806</a>"},{"pid":"82d79bc2000ee7c580d7bb62453d3632e072af5d","tid":2400440,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11a9c1eff2fe0b010c4fb1ba202a058f0853b940","tid":2400440,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a3f5b67459c00b9fbc4bad519ed720992d9dde93","tid":2400440,"uid":18477,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-